</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/_jNSfgP9zSw" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/06/global-pc-tablet-market-q3-2021-report/notebook/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=global-pc-tablet-market-q3-2021-report</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>安心出行平價手機推介，最平$700 有找 + 鴨寮街行情速遞</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/d_mMSQD-0n4/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 05 Nov 2021 12:47:59 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[安心出行]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1070053</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>自 11 月 1 日起出入政府場所要掃「安心出行」才可入內。令不少朋友都想為老人家買部平價手機，入街市掃碼之用 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>自 11 月 1 日起出入政府場所要掃「安心出行」才可入內。令不少朋友都想為老人家買部平價手機，入街市掃碼之用；不少朋友亦希望買多部手機專門用來掃「安心出行」。以下就推介市面上可以買到的平價手機，新機 700 至 800 元都有好多選擇。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070056" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-694x411.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="411" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-694x411.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-768x455.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005.jpg 963w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070057" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>好多人想入手平價手機，今日小編就來到鴨寮街留意行情，雖然是平日，但仍有好多人圍著手機店，大家都想買「安心出行」專用機。由於「安心出行」只是用來打卡用，並不耗電也不用很強的處理器，因此一眾 Android 舊機的全新貨品就極受歡迎。</p><h2>Nokia C01 PLUS 好多地方賣斷市 $699</h2><p>Nokia C01 PLUS 這部機還算新，運行 Android 11 配備有 5.45 吋熒幕，雖然處理器行 SC9863a，相機也只有 500 萬像素，不過它的價錢只售 HK$699，在好多地方都沽清。<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.43.42.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.43.50.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.43.50-694x502.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="502" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.43.50-694x502.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.43.50.jpg 723w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>小米出品 Redmi-9A 只售 $699</h2><p>想$700 以下出機，也可留意這部紅米 9A。它內置有 6.53 吋大熒幕，而且有 5000mAh 電池，可謂幾抵玩，其大電也適合用作副機，不用經常充電。現在這部機在官方網站已經無貨，不過大家仍能夠在市面部份地方找到。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.43.42.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070059" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.43.42-694x437.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="437" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.43.42-694x437.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.43.42-768x483.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.43.42.jpg 1174w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>uleFone Note 8P 鴨寮街熱賣 $690</h2><p>以上兩部手機未必在市面買到，而小編在鴨寮街留意行情，發現另一部只售$690-$780 的平價機 uleFone Note 8P 的手機仍然在多間店鋪有貨。這部機行 Android 10，晶片用上 MTK MT6737 SoC，內置有 5.5 吋熒幕，重量也只是 153g，輕便攜帶，相機更有 800 萬像素。香港行貨機，弄壞了也有保養。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-397x580.jpg" alt="" width="397" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-397x580.jpg 397w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009.jpg 515w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 397px" /></a></p><h2>華為 P Smart $738 有交易</h2><p>這部屬於國際版的華為 P Smart，可以用到 Google Play，下載安心出行無問題（當然華為 AppGallery 都可下載到「安心出行」，但好多朋友都問，其實只要是 Android 機都不用擔心）。它內置有 5.65 吋熒幕，最平一部賣 $738 行 Android 8.0。如果想買較新一部，可留意 2019 年推出的，華為 P Smart，同為國際版手機，不過就要 $999。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0013.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070064" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0013-597x580.jpg" alt="" width="597" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0013-597x580.jpg 597w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0013.jpg 685w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 597px" /></a></p><h2>華為 Y7 Pro 用高通 Snapdragon 430 只售 $788</h2><p>另外現在你仍可買到行 Android 8.0 的華為 Y7 Pro，它行 8 核心 Snapdragon 430 處理器，有雙卡雙待，支援 SD 卡，已內置有 32GB 容量，只售 $788。另外它有一部高階機華為 Y7 Prime，規格一樣，但就加入指紋辨識，在掃碼時解鎖更加方便，一樣有 Google Play，行鋪售價為 $888。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0011.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070066" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0011-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0011-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0011-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0011-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0011.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>華為 Nova 2 機仔細細適合當副機 $798</h2><p>如果你不嫌機款較舊，機仔薄薄，細細部的華為 Nova 2 也適合用來做「安心出行」專用機，它同樣有 Google Play，有指紋識別，行單 sim 卡，行 Kirin 659 八核心處理器，內置有 64GB 容量，它機身只有 5 吋熒幕。售價為 $798。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070067" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-677x580.jpg" alt="" width="677" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-677x580.jpg 677w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-768x658.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015.jpg 872w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 677px" /></a></p><h2>金屬外殼中階機 Nokia 6 只售 $898</h2><p>俾多少少錢，但現在你仍買到 Nokia 6 新機。它有 5.5 吋熒幕，畫面解像度去到 1920&#215;1080，相機解像度達 1600 萬像素，內置指紋解鎖同 NFC，這個配置俾老人家當主機都夠用。不過留意返它只安裝有 Android 7.1 作業系統。售價為 $898。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070061" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>Samsung 機都有 Galaxy A02 賣 $998</h2><p>想買 Samsung 機的話，你可在鴨寮街等地方買到 Samsung Galaxy A02，這部中階機內置有 5000mAh 大電池，適合不常充電，把它用來當「安心出行」機的朋友。此機行 Mediatek MT6739W，擁有 6.5 吋熒幕，具備有 1300 萬＋200 萬像素雙後置鏡頭，重量為 206g。此機在鴨寮街售價為 $998-1080。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>Nokia 5.4 大熱賣售價 $1,498</h2><p>如果你有點要求的話，可留意這部較新的機種 Nokia 5.4，它有 6.39 吋熒幕，行 Android 10，內置 Snapdragon 662 八核心處理器，而且已內置有 128GB 容量，電池又有 4000mAh。售價就會貴一點，賣$1,498。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070069" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012-694x470.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="470" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012-694x470.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012-768x520.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0012.jpg 967w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>想買平機，仲可以揀二手</h2><p>其實好多機都有二手貨賣，$680-$750 就可以買到 Samsung 機又或者小米機。Apple iPhone 的二手機雖然較為冒險，不過在 1000～1100 元左右你也可找到 iPhone 6S 等手機，俾得起 $1500 的話更可找到外觀不錯的 iPhone 8。不過留意購買二手機有一定風險，請大家自行斟酌。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070055" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-1-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0001-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>「安心出行」自己裝就得！不用靠人</h2><p style="text-align: left;">我們發現市面上有手機店以數十元裝機費，為老人家裝「安心出行」，其實用戶可以自己裝都得。現時「安心出行」在蘋果 App Store、Google Play 商店，以及華為 App Gallery 都可安裝。當然你需要事先在這些商店啟用帳戶才行。最多人有問題的 Android 手機，例如三星機、小米機、華為機，只要打開「設定」選單，選擇「Google」，你就可以建立新帳戶。建立好新帳戶後，打開「Play 商店」，搜尋「安心出行」就會找到。所以不需要俾錢給人幫你安裝！</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.49.19-1.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-52-46-946_com_android_settings.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070078" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-52-46-946_com_android_settings-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-52-46-946_com_android_settings-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-52-46-946_com_android_settings-506x900.jpg 506w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-52-46-946_com_android_settings-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-52-46-946_com_android_settings-864x1536.jpg 864w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-52-46-946_com_android_settings.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></a>▲在手機打開設定畫面就找到 Google<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-52-46-946_com_android_settings-1.png"><br /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-52-46-946_com_android_settings.png"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-53-13-707_com_google_android_gms.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070076" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-53-13-707_com_google_android_gms-327x580.png" alt="" width="327" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-53-13-707_com_google_android_gms-327x580.png 327w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-53-13-707_com_google_android_gms-508x900.png 508w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-53-13-707_com_google_android_gms-768x1360.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-53-13-707_com_google_android_gms-867x1536.png 867w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-53-13-707_com_google_android_gms.png 903w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 327px" /></a>▲如果你未有 Google 帳戶的話，按左下角的「建立帳戶」登記一個便可<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-54-06-303_com.android.vending.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070080" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-54-06-303_com.android.vending-326x580.png" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-54-06-303_com.android.vending-326x580.png 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-54-06-303_com.android.vending-506x900.png 506w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-54-06-303_com.android.vending-768x1365.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-54-06-303_com.android.vending-864x1536.png 864w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot_2021-11-05-19-54-06-303_com.android.vending.png 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></a>▲之後你就可打開「Play 商店」搜尋「安心出行」，或者搜尋「GovHK」就可找到「安心出行」應用程式安裝<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-05-19.49.19-1.jpg"><br /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
